{"tid":1745674,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"區選投票流程 ！！我唔夠秤 求下你出去投票","createTime":"2019-11-22T10:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T12:42:12.000Z","uid":46688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2049e39c15b826c0045169e3940203de2a342504","tid":1745674,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"區選投票流程 ！！我唔夠秤 求下你出去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整合各方資料同自己見解（希望冇漏）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關於11.24選舉投票流程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n📍票站開放時間：7:30am-10:30pm <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> （越早越好 避免正苦提早結束選舉而冇得投） </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n📍<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">衣著：❌黑衫 ❌黑口罩 </span></strong><br />\n📍有長者帶埋佢去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n📍記住帶身份證正本去投票卡指定票站投票<br />\n<br />\n📍唔知票站係邊？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/p_cs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fchi%2Fp_cs.html&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=e319c038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/p_cs.html</a><br />\n<br />\n📍入到票站唔好影相拍片<br />\n📍比身分證選管會職員check<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">攞到張票之後 1️⃣唔該check清楚張票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n⚠️如果有任何爛咗嘅地方 唔好要 唔係當<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">廢票</span></span><br />\n📍⚠️左上角有嗰切角位因為方便比視障人士用 不過應該唔代表其他位置⚠️<br />\n📌立即向嗰個票站嘅選舉主任投訴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n📌並且向ICAC舉報 <br />\n📌要選舉主任比張全新嘅選票比你<br />\n📌<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又再check 1次</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">2️⃣投票吸印仔請揀啱嘅人✅</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://vote4.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=9f498a81\" target=\"_blank\">vote4.hk</a> 👈呢個網答到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">📌投白票=浪費自己張選票+D手足嘅選票<br />\n投咗未必贏 你唔投一定輸<br />\n📌和勇不分 呢個係一個公投 一定要投黃 目標係踢走送中派 好簡單你會想揀一個朋友定一個仇人<br />\n📌輸咗國際戰線唔洗打</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: large;\">3️⃣投票吸印仔唔好心急 剩係吸一次✅</span><br />\n📌吹下佢 等佢完全乾之後先好對摺<br />\n尤其是朝早嗰印仔仲好濕<br />\n📌唔係個✅印埋落對面果頁就當廢票<br />\n📌最好就過<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">30</span></strong>秒先摺<br />\n📌<span style=\"color: red;\">之後仲要親自放落投票箱入面</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">4️⃣投完票出票站可能有建制民意調查嘅人問你投咗比邊個 </span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兩大方案</span><br />\n📌唔洗理佢哋 掂行掂過就得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />📌亂答 話投建制派 嗰D個人資料一樣亂答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n📍<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後最最最緊要梗係叫埋其他未投票嘅屋企人同朋友去投票 幾票已經可以改變好多 有D選區試過因為幾十票甚至幾票輸左比送中派</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n📍然後去黃店食個早餐翻去瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span><br />\n#和你投<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnHVeHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnHVeHq.png&h=75f4914e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cu2J72s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCu2J72s.png&h=d6e2afed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbxRxt8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbxRxt8.png&h=9c845071&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64f5eddfa12b92dff513ab3ce1db7097d830a0cc","tid":1745674,"uid":17419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>建制贏，POPO同班藍絲可以大大聲話民意喺佢地果邊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b1b26caf75968cc9052f794de49d38f76deb97cc","tid":1745674,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"【突發】WhatsGap 新推出選舉地圖 自己選區 侯選人資料一清二楚<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745395</a><br />\n-<br />\nWhatsGap 推出咗選舉地圖，入面仲有埋侯選人資料，俾大家參考！<br />\n希望大家多多支持、share、airdrop俾身邊朋友手足睇到，順便follow埋我哋FB同IG page！<br />\n-<br />\nFact check 網址：<a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=93c842f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io</a><br />\nWhatsGap FB：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/whatsgaphk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwhatsgaphk&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=75859bd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/whatsgaphk</a><br />\nWhatsGap IG ：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/whatsgaphk/?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwhatsgaphk%2F%3Fhl%3Den&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylqVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=ec54d572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/whatsgaphk/?hl=en</a>"},{"pid":"a5886f74126a68a195315aef5ca60c26fd4e0ad4","tid":1745674,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"投泛民"},{"pid":"ef248c682853491a78959d95a8de3716